{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"108823-hajuramako-gajjabko-mesin","title":"हजुरआमाको गज्जबको मेसिन","description":"सुरज र उसकी हजुरआमालाई नयाँ-नयाँ कुरा आविष्कार गर्न मन पर्छ । उनीहरुले नरिवलकाे बर्फि बनाउन सरल यन्त्रकाे प्रयाेग कसरी गरे, पढाैं है !","language":"Nepali","langCode":"ne","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Anbika Giri"],"illustrators":["Rajiv Eipe"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Sangrila Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/108823-hajuramako-gajjabko-mesin"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/712718/size3/9afb2c00f7a211ff4c8699e66ca7db0b.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/712718/size6/9afb2c00f7a211ff4c8699e66ca7db0b.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/30169/size6/d207276a2815a071558385c615a4b8cb.jpg","text":"“हजुरआमा ! हजुरआमा ! आज हामी नरिवलको\nबर्फी बनाउँ न है ?” सुरजले हजुरआमालाई कर गर्यो— “प्लिज !”","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/30284/size6/1f1845b3937db71d57097700da2554b1.jpg","text":"\"हेहेहे.... तिमीले सघायौ भने बनाउँछु, सघाउँछौ त ?” हजुरआमाले भन्नुभयो ।\n                                                                    \"हुर्रे !\"","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/30056/size6/a01635d8b9b4cd72c320d8fb5aa29cc2.jpg","text":"\"तपाईँ तयार हो ?\" सुरज चिच्च्यायाे ।\n\"हो हो !\" हजुरआमाले भन्नुभयो ।","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/30731/size6/5d387c832dfc2d8d6e086bf82f9e6269.jpg","text":"“पाकेको पाकेको छान्नुपर्छ है ! पुरै खैरो\nभइसकेको मात्र...\nहेर है ! लौ झर्यो, झर्यो !”\nड्याङ्ग","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/30060/size6/6c476755eef54f036cedb0b6fd497f0f.jpg","text":"\"अब बाहिरको खोस्टा फ्याँकौं…\"\n             \nख्यास् ! ख्यास् !","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/30279/size6/484adb7c7ebb9ebb4fdf2092c25e926f.jpg","text":"सुरजको पेट कराउँछः कुइँयऽ \nहजुरआमा खित्खित हाँस्नुहुन्छ ।","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/30062/size6/533efd06df4be288862d4e89ff04bc26.jpg","text":"“अब नरिवल फुटाऊँ !”\n                                                  कर्याक्क !","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/30732/size6/9e13646576c48649aecb5aa3c3efab5e.jpg","text":"\"कस्तो\nगगगज्ज्जज्बको नरिवल !\"","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/30152/size6/28802bc5377967007a502c69b077a3e1.jpg","text":"\"अब सबै मरमसला हालेर यसलाई राम्रोसँग चलाउनुपर्छ....\"\n“ओहो ! कस्तो मिठो बास्ना आको हजुरआमा !”","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/30734/size6/b95cb78abce35280c1ca70735be5d798.jpg","text":"“अब यसलाई एउटा भाँडामा खन्याउनुपर्छ ।\nसेलाउन्जेल पर्खौं है नाति !”","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/155878/size6/707bd178a51d822b56025671a7c9b599.jpg","text":"\"अब यसलाई स-साना  टुक्रामा\n       मिलाएर काट्नुपर्छ...\"\n                   \n                       चट्चट्चट्","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/30287/size6/c2ace437c2e968656969c7158d3b4ecf.jpg","text":"\"आहा ! हाम्राे बर्फी तयार भयाे ! अब खाए हुन्छ !\"\n                                             \n                                              \"कस्तो मिठो ! कस्तो मिठो !\"","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/30157/size6/69dd429e6d3e945223839ec85adf3f34.jpg","text":"हजुरआमाले सरल यन्त्र प्रयाेग गरेर बर्फी बनाउनुभयाे । सरल यन्त्रले हाम्राे कामलाई सजिलाे बनाउँछ । सरल यन्त्र छ प्रकारका छन् ः\n१. छड्के सतह\n२. उत्तोलक \n३. पाङ्ग्रा र बिँड","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/30159/size6/862c132774e3089a686ee8f1eb517986.jpg","text":"४. फेसाे\n५. घिर्नी \n६. पेच \nके तिमी आफ्नाे वरपर सुरज र हजुरआमाले बर्फी बनाउँदा  प्रयाेग गरेका सरल यन्त्र चिन्न सक्छौ ?","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":14,"words":189}}